	{"x4pointer":" "
	,"x4code":null
	,"x4freetext":["Thin film of natural Cu was fabricated on polished"
		," (100) silicon substrate. Just before evaporation the"
		,"Si substrate was cleaned with Ar+ ion sputtering. The"
		,"sample was further coated by thin gold film with 37 nm."
		,"The energy width of the copper sample film was 40 keV"
		,"for 3. MeV protons, thickness was 725 nm."]
	}
      ]
